<title>Mochi::FS::IFileLoader Class Reference</title>
<indexterm><primary>Mochi::FS::IFileLoader</primary></indexterm>
<para>

<para>Interface to get files that are part of the game data. Note that the interface does not have any save or write function. This is not meant to create persistent file systems, but to create virtual file systems from which to read. </para>
 
